ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRemission Order in Respect of Fees for Claims Filed under the Hazardous Materials Information Review Act for Exemption from the Requirement to Disclose Confidential Business Information
PrecisREMISSION ORDER IN RESPECT OF FEES FOR CLAIMS FILED UNDER THE HAZARDOUS MATERIALS INFORMATION REVIEW ACT FOR EXEMPTION FROM THE REQUIREMENT TO DISCLOSE CONFIDENTIAL BUSINESS INFORMATION in order to remit fees paid by eligible regulated companies when seeking exemption from Confidiential Business Information disclosure requirements that are no longer required.
